json example:
        {"word":"prospect ",
        "phonetic":"[ˈprɒspekt]","speech":"v. & n. ",
        "explanation":"展望；前景 ",
        "example":"eg. She's a good prospect for the national team.\n她是国家队的未来。\n\nP.S 小艾最近有些忙，抱歉且非常感谢支持，开学后会第一时间完善功能！^ ^ "}
